Satu lagi kerugian?

250
00:20:01,074 --> 00:20:02,284
Awak pula?

251
00:20:02,367 --> 00:20:04,703
Siapa Woo-seong bagi awak?

252
00:20:05,704 --> 00:20:06,872
Apa maksud awak?

253
